line_2: They have pierc'd through the crumbling Mould,

line_1: In them redeem your errours manifold;
line_2: In vain and sensual habits now grown old,

line_1: In them redeem your errours manifold;
line_2: Nor re-assume at will your native mould,

line_1: In them redeem your errours manifold;
line_2: Yet envy not the state, you could not hold;
